OL,3,C'No chequebook yet' for Sadiq Khan as
OL,4,Cmayor seeks long term transport funding
OL,6,FSadiq Khan might have to wait a bit
OL,7,Flonger to get the money he wants to
OL,8,Fbankroll Transport for London after
OL,9,Fbeing told by the Transport Secretary
OL,10,F"I've not come with my chequebook".
OL,12,FLondon's mayor reportedly needs #500m-
OL,13,Fa-year from the government and a long
OL,14,Fterm funding deal to make sure the
OL,15,Fcapital's buses and Tubes run smoothly.
OL,17,FBut Labour's new Transport Secretary
OL,18,Fsaid any settlement would come at the
OL,19,Fend of a comprehensive spending review
OL,20,Fand Budget at the end of the year.
