OL,3,C'No chequebook yet' for Sadiq Khan as
OL,4,Cmayor seeks long term transport funding
OL,6,FLouise Haigh MP added: "Sadiq and I
OL,7,Fhave a really good relationship
OL,8,Falready, and I wanted to come down and
OL,9,Fsee him early on to demonstrate that
OL,10,Fthis government is going to work very
OL,11,Fdifferently with London and TfL.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately, I've not come with my
OL,14,Fchequebook today.
OL,16,F"We want to work in partnership
OL,17,Fbecause we want to deliver for London.
OL,18,FAnd we know that spending in London
OL,19,Fsupports the rest of the country as
OL,20,Fwell.
