OL,3,C'No chequebook yet' for Sadiq Khan as
OL,4,Cmayor seeks long term transport funding
OL,6,F"But we absolutely want to look to
OL,7,Fmore multi-year settlements. We know
OL,8,Fthat allows local authorities and
OL,9,Fmayors to plan ahead and deliver
OL,10,Fbetter services."
OL,12,FA longer term finance agreement would
OL,13,Fmake it easier and more efficient to
OL,14,Fbuy big-ticket items such as new
OL,15,Ftrains.
OL,17,FThe amount Sadiq Khan wants is twice
OL,18,Fthe #250m given to TfL under the
OL,19,FConservatives for the 2024-25
OL,20,Ffinancial year.
