OL,3,C'No chequebook yet' for Sadiq Khan as
OL,4,Cmayor seeks long term transport funding
OL,6,F"What we want is firstly a long term
OL,7,Fdeal," Mr Khan said.
OL,9,F"The amount of money depends in
OL,10,Frelation to the ambitions that
OL,11,Fgovernment has in relation to growth.
OL,13,F"We think we can help with the
OL,14,Fobjective the government has to get
OL,15,Fgrowth across the country. We know
OL,16,Fthere are 100,000 jobs across the
OL,17,Fcountry supported by TfL," Mr Khan
OL,18,Fexplained.
