OL,3,C'No chequebook yet' for Sadiq Khan as
OL,4,Cmayor seeks long term transport funding
OL,6,FIn the past a shortfall in funding had
OL,7,Fled to doubts over TfL's ability to go
OL,8,Fahead with projects such as the
OL,9,Fproposed Bakerloo line upgrade and
OL,10,Fextension.
OL,12,FMr Khan added: "Over the course of the
OL,13,Flast two weeks I've met the Prime
OL,14,Fminister, the Deputy Prime Minister,
OL,15,Fthe Chancellor, the Environment
OL,16,FSecretary.
OL,18,F"Now, this morning, the Transport
OL,19,FSecretary. That's refreshing for me.
